    positive: |-
      One notable strength was the strong organization of the report and the thoughtful way the final deliverable connected the analysis back to the app design scenario.
      One area for improvement would be adding more detailed interpretation to a few of the graphs and discussing why the observed patterns are important.
    negative: One area for improvement would be adding more detailed interpretation
      to a few of the graphs and discussing why the observed patterns are important.
    advice: The submission could be improved by expanding the written interpretation
      for the visualizations, adding a little more stylistic polish to the charts,
      and including one of the optional extra credit components.
  scores:
